[Zeke] Yeah, I haven't really
been able to do anything else.

1:04:01.867 --> 1:04:03.300
[chuckling]

1:04:03.300 --> 1:04:07.100
I don't really know
if you can do anything else
after doing that.

1:04:07.166 --> 1:04:09.867
There's no other job
where you're just
picking up money.

1:04:09.867 --> 1:04:12.300
Yeah, no.
